org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace

  • Packages that use org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace 
    Package Description
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.clc.cas.consed  
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed
    This package contains classes for working with Consed.
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace
    This package contains classes for handling Contigs stored in the Ace File Format.
  • Classes in org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace used by org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.clc.cas.consed 
    Class and Description
    AceContig
    an AceContig is a Contig from an ace file.
    AceContigBuilder
    Builder for AceContigs that allows creating AceContig objects read by read by adding assembled reads and setting a consensus.
    PhdInfo
    PhdInfo is a value class that contains information to link an ace read to a record in the corresponding phd file.

  • Classes in org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace used by org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace 
    Class and Description
    AbstractAceContigVisitor
    AbstractAceContigVisitor is an AceContigVisitor that implements all the methods as stubs.
    AceAssembledRead
    AceAssembledRead is a AssembledRead implementation specific for reads from an ace file.
    AceAssembledReadBuilder
    AceAssembledReadBuilder is a Builder for AceAssembledReads for a specific AceContig.
    AceConsensusTagVisitor 
    AceContig
    an AceContig is a Contig from an ace file.
    AceContigBuilder
    Builder for AceContigs that allows creating AceContig objects read by read by adding assembled reads and setting a consensus.
    AceContigReadVisitor 
    AceContigVisitor 
    AceFileDataStore
    AceFileDataStore is a ContigDataStore for AceContigs that are contained in a single .ace file.
    AceFileDataStoreBuilder
    AceFileDataStoreBuilder is a builder that can create new AceFileDataStore instances using data from a given ace file.
    AceFileVisitor
    AceFileVisitor is a Visitor implementation for .ace encoded assembly files.
    AceFileVisitorCallback 
    AceFileVisitorCallback.AceFileVisitorMemento
    AceFileVisitorMemento is a marker interface that AceFileParser instances can use to "rewind" back to the position in its ace file in order to revisit portions of the ace file.
    AceFileWriter
    AceFileWriter handles writing out assembly data in ace format.
    AceFileWriterBuilder
    AceFileWriterBuilder is a builder for creating new AceFileWriter instances that handles writing out correctly formatted ace files that can be viewed with consed.
    AceParser
    AceParser is an interface that will parse an Ace structure and call the appropriate visit methods on the given AceFileVisitor.
    AceTag
    Ace files can contain tags at the end of the file which can inform consed tools of various features or hints or additional information that can not be explained in the standard ace file format.
    ConsensusAceTag
    ConsensusAceTag is an AceTag that maps to a particular location on the consensus of a contig in an ace file.
    ConsensusAceTagBuilder
    ConsensusAceTagBuilder is a Builder that builds a new instance of ConsensusAceTag.
    HighLowAceContigPhdDatastore.Builder
    Builder class to customize how creating the objects in the PhdDataStore from the ace file.
    PhdInfo
    PhdInfo is a value class that contains information to link an ace read to a record in the corresponding phd file.
    RangeableAceTag
    RangeableAceTag is a version of an AceTag that maps to a particular location on a genomic element in the assembly.
    ReadAceTag
    ReadAceTag is an AceTag that maps to a particular location on a specific read of a contig in an ace file.
    WholeAssemblyAceTag
    A WholeAssemblyAceTag is an AceTag that applies to the entire assembly in the ace file usually these types of tags refer to things like where the phdball is located.
